newsitem.title: NEW ZEALAND: NZ 98-day T-bills yield 8.693 pct at tender.
newsitem.headline: NZ 98-day T-bills yield 8.693 pct at tender.

text.p: The weighted average yield for NZ$75 million of 98-day treasury bills at Tuesday's tender was 8.693 percent versus 9.200 percent for the NZ$75 million of a similar maturity at last week's tender, the Reserve Bank said.
